Lisa K. Wyatt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_K._Wyatt 0 Lisa K. Wyatt is an American actress and comedian. According to the biography on her official site, she has appeared in more than 150 film, television and regional theatre credits. In the show's fifth season, she was hired for the recurring role as Lynne, the love interest of Kevin Malone, in NBC's The Office. Lisa_K._Wyatt is an_American_actress_and_comedian .
